{"tid":1473573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國文宣 - 外國人支持我哋，咁你想外國人點做","createTime":"2019-08-15T01:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T02:16:15.000Z","uid":148390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe49626d1aed3c4ccfdee7462788fa3b4343a88","tid":1473573,"uid":148390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:31:05.000Z","msg":"頭先睇左個post<br />\n<br />\n外國人心聲︰得喇我知香港喇，咁我可以點幫手呀大佬？你講至得架！點幫呀？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1472787\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1472787</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我覺得重點係外國 「人」 可以做咩<br />\n唔係外國政府可以做咩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我明白大家嘅最終目標都係想外國政府幫手，外國政府制裁中國，外國政府封黑官財產，外國政府唔比黑警入境等等<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係想幫手嘅係外國「人」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n姐係咁<br />\n你facebook見到有人好慘<br />\n你問佢有咩幫到手<br />\n佢答你：你幫我制裁個政府啦<br />\n你會點諗？<br />\n「制裁個政府？點制裁呀？」<br />\n「哇，國際政治野唔關我事」<br />\n「on9，當我係雜種？」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">正確方向</span><br />\n<br />\n1.幫手整定唔同國家嘅聯署比佢地簽<br />\n我哋簽左咁多白官聯署，唔可以話冇用，但始終係要求幫助<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但如果係美國人聯署叫美國政府幫我地呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n（可行性未fc，發起人可能要當地人）<br />\n<br />\n2.發起ig 我支持香港示威者運動<br />\n類似冰桶果啲，叫佢地公開表達支持我地<br />\n整定啲文宣圖比佢地post<br />\n<br />\n有巴打提醒唔好膠化，我覺得可以純支持加發表意見，支國護旗手都得，我哋可以connect全世界<br />\n<br />\n3.甚至叫佢地捐錢<br />\n<br />\n認同就幫手推到文宣見到"},{"pid":"d2c461dffbf3aec64b8660b17f5db7b3891f188b","tid":1473573,"uid":148390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:32:05.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"dc33e33b79223cdadacea1be133f5a768d8ccb3d","tid":1473573,"uid":148390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:34:29.000Z","msg":"自推9"},{"pid":"40a884c230455d80350c6912e5bd95d826261949","tid":1473573,"uid":148390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:36:30.000Z","msg":"自推8"},{"pid":"eb1f7d0b5e8726cbd99e561544423ec68cc31786","tid":1473573,"uid":148390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:39:22.000Z","msg":"自推7"},{"pid":"c865eae250fd9c7d8fe52bb03e8701b43c3b5c6e","tid":1473573,"uid":161193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:41:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>擺買中國貨</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b4b18ad7e073e85937a657b9d3a1edb44641152b","tid":1473573,"uid":257087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:42:31.000Z","msg":"可以既，捐錢未必最好，oversea payment佢地一定會擔心啲錢點用，但聯署係一個好方法。"},{"pid":"63075bea0b1b112652d9f2e881fecf40508d16c0","tid":1473573,"uid":148390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:46:44.000Z","msg":"自推6 <br />\n<br />\n818見"},{"pid":"0d142515999616335be14d33e6478f26366f216f","tid":1473573,"uid":307270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:49:19.000Z","msg":"818 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca0b6ffc19fb8cb367cff28bbb26990b003b00d","tid":1473573,"uid":148390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:55:13.000Z","msg":"自推5<br />\n721 811<br />\n<br />\n818見"},{"pid":"6d26fdce15498b1598832fb7d0e0a5490aa5b5c3","tid":1473573,"uid":224018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:57:23.000Z","msg":"外國記者多報導 香港正面新聞 就算幫助"},{"pid":"c9d0de7dde646145e882244417a0c5f1eb4ee4ab","tid":1473573,"uid":307270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:58:31.000Z","msg":"suggest 發起 IG切個洋蔥 challenge<br />\n參加者要戴上口罩 然後切洋蔥<br />\n要切到流眼水 模擬食TG<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /